Cell["\<\
The fully-contracted term(s) processed henceforth correspond to \
fully-contracted  disjoint Bogoliubov contribution(s) generated by the \
application of Wick\[CloseCurlyQuote]s theorem to the following matrix \
element (cf. expansion formula of Gorkov\[CloseCurlyQuote]s polarization \
propagator), \
\>", "Text",
