Cell["\<\
Times are sorted in ascending order: \[OpenCurlyQuote]2\[CloseCurlyQuote] (\
\[OpenCurlyQuote]1\[CloseCurlyQuote]) is the latest time and denotes t (t\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8883167440333986`*^9, 3.88831696819341*^9}, {
